---
title: Scrambled Eggs
image: https://imgs.search.brave.com/dvzU-UmihZM61yQQ2-qeEWtfH3YWjjgOcsjnfQPPMrs/rs:fit:860:0:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly90b3Jp/YXZleS5jb20vaW1h/Z2VzLzIwMTkvMDgv/SU1HXzk5MDQuanBl/Zw
---

Crack @eggs{8} into a bowl with @salt{}.

Melt @butter{15%g} in a #pan over low heat.

Add the eggs and stir gently until just set, about ~{5%minutes}.
